title: DDFP: Yup, we're talking Playoffs.
itunes:title: DDFP: Yup, we're talking Playoffs.
description:
We are officially at the halfway point of the NFL season so the fellas welcome back Zach “The Blue Horseshoe” Rosenfield of Accuscore.com to look back at the preseason pro-Shek-tions and take a gander at the playoff landscape in both pro and college football. Rank also tries to defend his misguided notion that Magic Johnson was the greatest player in NBA history. It’s a thin slice of heaven, won’t you listen? 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
